een": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "1138650935"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q892495", "wikipedia_page_title": "Boniface de Challant", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "C", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/de/articles/013131/2005-02-16"}